result.name: Café Hunan

reviews.text: Used to be very good. However, the quality is surprisingly going downhill so quickly these two years. Food is oily and look similar from one another
Spicy spicy! Good fix like you love hot food. This is a Michelin recommended place to eat.
Great human food! Especially liked the fried chicken cartilage with red chili peppers.

Small place, staff know enough English to serve you the right food, greasy floors though, but everything else was fine. The food had great flavours but most of them tasted the same - chilli.  Would recommend but maybe get some noodles or rice to neutralize the spicy-ness. The coconut milk drink  was great (and helps with the chilli).
The reason i missed Hong kong! all the food were Amazing in this place! best is when you eat with your friends.
